Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,{\a6}Daichi-kun and his siblings let me play with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:27.76,Default,Daichi,0,0,0,,We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.03,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:30.59,Default,Yuna & Kuta,0,0,0,,Friends, friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:33.60,Default,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It's dinner time. Let's go home.
