Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.50,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Don't go near that man again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:39.16,Default,Daichi,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.15,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,He's what you call \Na suspicious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:42.11,Default,Daichi,0,0,0,,Suspicious person?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.40,Default,Daichi,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Mister Suspicious Person!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:46.88,Default,Sorata,0,0,0,,Bye, suspicious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:47.80,Default,Yuna,0,0,0,,Suspicious person!
