Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.22,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Huh? "Suspicious person"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.21,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Oh... No, you've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong.
