Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.09,0:42:51.33,Bengoshi-Top,LadYoshie,0,0,0,,Get your hands \Noff my husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.19,0:42:55.90,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,Unofficial wife {\c&H6D39DC&}VS {\c&HFF6BFD&}official wife
