Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.46,0:42:55.90,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Right,Caption,0,0,0,,Which one is the real wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.58,0:42:54.94,Bengoshi-Top,Lady2,0,0,0,,I'm his wife!
